author: Project Veritas
description:
Project Veritas’ "Without Consent Part 2" investigation unveils Elvira Syed’s heart-wrenching testimony, accusing Reverend Aaron Miller, a transgender pastor in Hartford, Connecticut, of manipulating DCF to fracture her family, ultimately contributing to the tragic death of her daughter, Ilene Syed.

“I heard about Pastor Aaron Miller from a DCF (Department of Children and Family) social worker. Aaron Miller filed a complaint against me after he saw my daughter only once for emotional abuse because I was refusing to affirm her gender identity due to my Muslim beliefs.”

“If it was not [for] Pastor Miller, if he did not put the wedge between me and my daughter, my daughter would be still alive.”
